that you understand

13:35.182 --> 13:37.048
That black people don't
just randomly start dancing.

13:37.050 --> 13:39.217
No, I mean this is -- this is
a very big moment for dre.

13:39.219 --> 13:41.052
♪ roast-roast
ro-roast-roasted them ♪

13:41.054 --> 13:47.058
Sweetheart, I fell asleep trying
to<i> put</i> someone to sleep today.

13:47.060 --> 13:48.960
