13:48.962 --> 13:52.096
I found your old teddy
and your old blanket.

13:52.098 --> 13:54.432
You feel safe now.
I need you to feel safe.

13:54.434 --> 13:57.001
You have to feel safe.
No one's safe.

13:57.003 --> 13:59.404
Night is coming.
Diane!

13:59.406 --> 14:02.907
You don't need to feel afraid
in your own house.

14:02.909 --> 14:05.510
It's not like this is
the hotel from "the shining."

14:05.512 --> 14:07.045
What's "the shining"?
Nothing.

14:07.047 --> 14:09.447
Mommy's tired.
Forget I mentioned it.

14:09.449 --> 14:12.317
Well, well, well,
"friend."

14:12.319 --> 14:16.955
How does knowing how to read
<i>so good</i> help you in the dark?

14:16.957 --> 14:17.922
Jack, stop it.

14:17.924 --> 14:19.023
I'm just saying.

14:19.025 --> 14:21.459
You were the first
to ride a bike,

14:21.461 --> 14:23.995
You were the first
to pee standing up.
Wait, what?

14:23.997 --> 14:26.197
Well, I'm the first one
not to be afraid of the dark.

14:26.199 --> 14:28.233
How does it feel,
little baby scaredy cat?

14:28.235 --> 14:30.602
Okay, jack,
that is not appropriate.

14:30.604 --> 14:32.036
I'll say.
Yep.

14:32.038 --> 14:33.605
"little
baby scaredy cat"?

14:33.607 --> 14:34.606
You hearing this, dad?

14:34.608 --> 14:36.040
Son,
that was weak sauce.

14:36.042 --> 14:37.475
Jack,
we're johnson men.

14:37.477 --> 14:39.644
We have a duty
to be good at roasting.
What?

14:39.646 --> 14:41.546
So instead, you should've said
something like,

14:41.548 --> 14:44.282
"nice glasses.
You look like --

14:44.284 --> 14:46.117
Like the world's
youngest librarian."

14:46.119 --> 14:47.452
Jack and junior: Ohh!
Okay, okay.

14:47.454 --> 14:49.087
Okay, no, no, no, no,
you're not helping.

14:49.089 --> 14:50.889
Uh!
I am exhausted.

14:50.891 --> 14:52.957
We need to
get her to sleep, okay?

14:52.959 --> 14:54.492
I hear you on the sleep.

14:54.494 --> 14:57.528
You're so tired, you look
like -- like you drowned.

14:57.530 --> 15:01.332
<i>Twice!</i>
[ guys cheering ]

15:02.902 --> 15:04.636
You don't just have bags
under your eyes,

15:04.638 --> 15:05.937
You've got...Luggage.

15:05.939 --> 15:07.472
[ guys cheering ]

15:07.474 --> 15:08.940
Samsonite!

15:08.942 --> 15:10.909
[ laughter ]
gimme three times!

15:10.911 --> 15:12.277
Both:
One, two, three.

15:12.279 --> 15:14.946
Why are you doing this?!

15:14.948 --> 15:17.515
Bow, this is the dozens,
all right?

15:17.517 --> 15:20.585
We come from a long,
proud african tradition of --

15:20.587 --> 15:22.954
Men who don't sleep
with their wives?

15:22.956 --> 15:25.423
All right, buddy, come here.
Let me talk to you about timing.

15:25.425 --> 15:26.925
Come here, come here.

15:26.927 --> 15:28.226
No.

15:28.228 --> 15:29.227
Mommy?

15:29.229 --> 15:30.561
No. No.

15:30.563 --> 15:31.562
Mom.
No.

15:35.067 --> 15:36.534
Hey, bow. Hey, babe.

15:36.536 --> 15:37.936
No.

15:37.938 --> 15:39.337
See?

15:39.339 --> 15:41.572
See how cute
junior used to be

15:41.574 --> 15:43.474
Before you taught him to say
I look like I drowned?!

15:43.476 --> 15:45.176
You're right, baby.
He shouldn't have said that.

15:45.178 --> 15:46.678
He shouldn't have said it.

15:46.680 --> 15:48.046
But have you looked
in the mirror?

15:48.048 --> 15:50.014
Fix him!
Junior!

15:50.016 --> 15:53.017
<i>Bow was right.</i>
<i>I may have created a monster.</i>

15:53.019 --> 15:57.088
<i>I had to make sure junior knew</i>
<i>how to talk trash responsibly.</i>

15:57.090 --> 15:58.389
All right, son.

15:58.391 --> 16:00.425
This is the most proud
you've ever made me,

16:00.427 --> 16:02.527
But I'm also
disappointed in you.

16:02.529 --> 16:07.332
Son, you made the women
in the house cry, but...

16:07.334 --> 16:09.000
You carried on my legacy.

16:09.002 --> 16:11.035
Those are
some very mixed messages.

16:11.037 --> 16:13.004
The point is
you went too far.

16:13.006 --> 16:14.472
I'm just doing
what you taught me, dad.

16:14.474 --> 16:17.075
Look, cody comes back
to school tomorrow,

16:17.077 --> 16:18.676
So I did
a background check on him.

16:18.678 --> 16:20.311
His dad
moved back to boston,

16:20.313 --> 16:21.713
And now his mom's
on tinder.

16:21.715 --> 16:25.416
[ laughs ] she's lonely.
Son, slow down, all right?

16:25.418 --> 16:27.185
That's some
deeply personal stuff.

16:27.187 --> 16:30.054
Look, man, I taught you
the dozens to defend yourself,

16:30.056 --> 16:31.422
Not go on the attack.

16:31.424 --> 16:34.525
And you should only use this
on people who can handle it,

16:34.527 --> 16:36.027
Otherwise,
<i>you</i> become the bully.

16:36.029 --> 16:38.529
Believe me,
cody can handle it.

16:38.531 --> 16:40.765
And he deserves it.
He's made my life miserable.

16:40.767 --> 16:42.600
Fine.

16:42.602 --> 16:44.602
Just remember
you have a choice --

16:44.604 --> 16:46.304
You can use
your gift wisely...

16:47.639 --> 16:50.375
...Or you can be
like darth vader and
go to the dark side.

16:50.377 --> 16:53.511
Darth vader didn't go
to the dark side.

16:53.513 --> 16:55.680
It was actually anakin
who went to the dark side

16:55.682 --> 16:57.749
And became darth vader
once he was there.

16:57.751 --> 17:00.018
Dad, where are you going?!

17:00.020 --> 17:01.686
You should really
watch the movies with me.

17:01.688 --> 17:04.122
You're gonna be extremely lost
when the new one comes out.

17:04.124 --> 17:06.758
[ door slams ]

17:06.760 --> 17:09.327
You've come a long way,
junior.

17:09.329 --> 17:12.030
I mean, I've actually admitted
to people that we're cousins.

17:12.032 --> 17:13.031
Wait, what?

17:13.033 --> 17:15.333
You haven't earned
"brother" yet.

17:15.335 --> 17:16.234
Cody: Hey, geek!

17:16.236 --> 17:18.169
[ crowd oohs ]

17:18.171 --> 17:20.038
Hey, cody, I'm here
to finish what we started.

17:20.040 --> 17:21.105
All of a sudden you think
you're the man?

17:21.107 --> 17:22.273
'cause you got jokes?

17:22.275 --> 17:25.410
I don't have any jokes today,
just facts.

17:25.412 --> 17:27.178
[ crowd murmuring ]

17:27.180 --> 17:30.081
Guess who I found
on tinder?

17:31.083 --> 17:33.351
Please.
Please don't do this, okay?

17:33.353 --> 17:37.088
Send a screenshot
to the whole school?

17:37.090 --> 17:38.423
[ crowd cheering ]

17:43.796 --> 17:46.497
Well, tell us --
who'd you find on tinder?

17:50.069 --> 17:52.603
You know who I found
on tinder?

17:52.605 --> 17:54.205
[ crowd cheering ]

17:54.207 --> 17:55.706
I found a --

17:55.708 --> 17:58.843
A bunch of girls
who<i> aren't</i> interested in me.

17:58.845 --> 18:00.244
[ laughs ]

18:00.246 --> 18:03.714
And why would they be
with these, uh...

18:03.716 --> 18:07.285
These, uh,
linguine arms?

18:07.287 --> 18:11.122
What do you cook these for?
Two, three minutes?

18:11.124 --> 18:14.292
I look like I should be
standing in front of a --

18:14.294 --> 18:16.594
In front of
an auto dealership.

18:16.596 --> 18:21.099
No money down
on all 2014s!

18:21.101 --> 18:23.334
Everything must go!

18:23.336 --> 18:26.170
No credit, no problem!

18:27.773 --> 18:30.741
Dude, that
was pretty classy.

18:30.743 --> 18:32.276
It felt good
to do the right --

18:33.846 --> 18:35.246
[ gasps ]

18:35.248 --> 18:37.782
It was your mom!
Your mom's on tinder!

18:37.784 --> 18:39.317
If you love mommy,

18:39.319 --> 18:43.121
You will go to sleep tonight
without the night-light.

18:43.123 --> 18:47.191
Actually, it's okay
if we use the night-light.

18:47.193 --> 18:48.826
Wait, really?

18:48.828 --> 18:51.762
Yeah, can we also leave
the lamp on and the door open?

18:51.764 --> 18:53.631
Hold on a second.
What's happening here?

18:53.633 --> 18:55.633
Does god listen to me?
Can you hear me, god?

18:55.635 --> 18:59.770
I may have tricked him
into watching "the shining."

19:01.406 --> 19:03.141
Aaaaah!

19:03.143 --> 19:05.576
Your sister dared you
to watch "the shining"?

19:05.578 --> 19:07.211
Yeah.

19:07.213 --> 19:09.881
So you are too scared
to sleep without a night-light?

19:09.883 --> 19:10.815
Yeah.

19:10.817 --> 19:12.250
Thank you.

19:12.252 --> 19:14.152
Mommy is gonna
sleep tonight,

19:14.154 --> 19:16.187
[ angrily ] and your brother
is gonna need therapy.

19:16.189 --> 19:18.523
You are a very bad --
good girl.

19:18.525 --> 19:20.825
You and daddy give
a lot of mixed messages.

19:20.827 --> 19:23.828
You're grounded tomorrow,
and I'm gonna get you a pony.

19:23.830 --> 19:25.897
Good night, babies.
Mommy's going to sleep.

19:25.899 --> 19:27.331
[ sighs ]

19:28.400 --> 19:31.636
Hey, sorry.
Sorry you got molly-whopped.

19:31.638 --> 19:32.904
