20:48.848 --> 20:51.315
Mm.

20:51.317 --> 20:53.751
Hello?
Yes, this is dr. Johnson.

20:53.753 --> 20:56.020
No, no, no.
No, I was not sleeping.

20:56.022 --> 20:59.557
I'm at the, um...Gym on the --
I'm on the treadmill.

20:59.559 --> 21:00.891
Okay.

21:03.262 --> 21:04.629
[ gasps ]

21:07.933 --> 21:10.268
Both: Come sleep with us.

21:10.270 --> 21:11.969
Come sleep with us forever.

21:17.743 --> 21:21.912
